OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1773259871
OL,3,COnline backlash over post showing
OL,4,Cvandalism of Guernsey park
OL,6,FA social media post displaying
OL,7,F'vandalism' at Delancey Park in
OL,8,FGuernsey has sparked an online
OL,9,Fbacklash, with some islanders
OL,10,Fsympathetic to the public damage.
OL,12,FThe Facebook post from the Constables
OL,13,Fof St Sampson's Parish showed an area
OL,14,Fof the park being "dug up to create
OL,15,Framps and hollows."
OL,17,FIt has since been taken down, due to
OL,18,Fabusive comments directed at parish
OL,19,Fstaff.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1773259871
OL,3,COnline backlash over post showing
OL,4,Cvandalism of Guernsey park
OL,6,FBut some islanders responded
OL,7,Fsympathetically to the damage, as it
OL,8,Fwas caused by adolescents seeking to
OL,9,Fcarve out tracks on which to ride
OL,10,Fmountain bikes.
OL,12,FOne user, Mark Smith, who is part of
OL,13,FGuernsey's Pumptrack Project, said
OL,14,Fonline that he 'understood' why
OL,15,Fteenagers in Guernsey might be drawn
OL,16,Fto dig up parts of the park.
OL,18,FSpeaking to ITV News, Mr Smith said:
OL,19,F"It's a shame kids are being vilified
OL,20,Ffor getting out and being active, when
OL,21,Fthat's what we want them to do.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1773259871
OL,3,COnline backlash over post showing
OL,4,Cvandalism of Guernsey park
OL,6,F"They're not breaking anything,
OL,7,Fthey're not ripping out trees or
OL,8,Fsmashing windows.
OL,10,F"They're trying to build a facility
OL,11,Ffor active recreation, rather than
OL,12,Fbeing indoors on video games or social
OL,13,Fmedia."
OL,15,FPlans to build a pump track for
OL,16,Fmountain biking on disused tennis
OL,17,Fcourts in Delancey Park were approved
OL,18,Fin September 2023, but construction
OL,19,Fhas yet to begin.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1773259871
OL,3,COnline backlash over post showing
OL,4,Cvandalism of Guernsey park
OL,6,FA pump track is a continuous circular
OL,7,Ftrack involving steep hills and banked
OL,8,Fturns for mountain bikes.
OL,10,FThere are bicycle tracks around
OL,11,FDelancey Park built by the Guernsey
OL,12,FMountain Bike Association (GMBA), but
OL,13,Fthese are not currently available for
OL,14,Fuse by cyclists, other than during
OL,15,Fmarshalled events held by Guernsey
OL,16,FVelo Club.
OL,18,FThis is because Guernsey's Places of
OL,19,FRecreation Ordinance from 1975
OL,20,Fdictates that no one above the age of
OL,21,Ften can ride a bicycle in the park.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1773259871
OL,3,COnline backlash over post showing
OL,4,Cvandalism of Guernsey park
OL,6,FITV News understands that discussions
OL,7,Fbetween the GMBA and Guernsey's
OL,8,Fauthorities to change the Ordinance to
OL,9,Fallow older cyclists to ride around
OL,10,Fthe park have broken down.
OL,12,FPaul Watts, Douzenier for the Parish
OL,13,Fof St Sampson, still believes the lack
OL,14,Fof usable cycle paths does not justify
OL,15,Fcriminal activity.
OL,17,FHe said: "Just because the new track
OL,18,Fhasn't happened, isn't an excuse to
OL,19,Fdamage public property."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
