CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1773259871
OL,3,COnline backlash over post showing
OL,4,Cvandalism of Guernsey park
OL,6,F"People would find it unacceptable if
OL,7,Fsomeone walked in their garden and
OL,8,Fstarted digging a hole.
OL,10,F"The holes have been dug on the
OL,11,Ffootpath, and there isn't any lighting
OL,12,Fin the park, so anyone walking in the
OL,13,Fpark now has an extra extra obstacle
OL,14,Fof a foot-deep hole where they
OL,15,Fwouldn't expect to find one."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/7
